project:
Fight as the mental mage in this never ending game! Use the arrow keys to move yourself around the area avoiding monsters. Use left click to fire a spell and right click to cycle through available spells, you can see a preview of the spell are currently using on the top left.

    At the end of a wave you are brought to your inventory. The grid is your mind, by placing spells there you can use them in combat.  You can unequip spells to make more space by dropping them on the right. You start with just a basic spell, but after every wave you complete you have a chance to learn a new spell. 

    When you continue to use the same spell, you learn it better. If you use it a certain amount of times in a wave, this causes the spell to increase in power - but also take up more space in your mind. This growth can cause spells to overlap, which results in one of the spells being pushed out of your mind. You can keep track of how many times in a wave you have used a spell with the gauge underneath the spell preview. If over-used, a spell may completely vanish all together so be careful and balance the usage of your spells!
